title: Thom Hartmann Program with Mike Newcomb - November 12 2013
description:
November 12, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

In for Thom today, please welcome Dr. Mike Newcomb, The Mike Newcomb Show, 1480AM KPHX, Phoenix, AZ

Hour One: Latest on Obamacare - Wendell Potter / Plus, Relief efforts underway in the Philippines - Lindsay Murphy, Mercy Corps

Hour Two: What candidates can learn from last week's elections - Heather Smith, Rock the Vote / Plus, ENDA and the free market - Peter Sprigg, Family Research Council

Hour Three: What you need to know about ENDA - Karl Frisch, Bullfight Strategies
